FBIS3-16661 "drsov053_s_94005" FBIS-SOV-94-053 Document Type:Daily Report 17 Mar 1994 Georgia Abkhaz Separatists Cut Off Gali Rayon LD1703125494 Tbilisi Radio Tbilisi Network in Georgian 0920 GMT 17 Mar 94 LD1703125494 Tbilisi Radio Tbilisi Network Language: Georgian Article Type:BFN [Text] The Abkhaz separatists have staged another adventure. Under the pretext of avoiding the spread of an infectious disease, they declared a quarantine on the whole of the territory of Gali rayon, thus making it impossible for relatives on either side of the Enguri river to visit each other.
